#

Peanut Sauce

10 min
$2.5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

PeanutsSoy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Sauce/Dressing

Tags:

SauceDressingDip

Description

A creamy and rich sauce that adds a delicious peanut flavor to your dishes.

Ingredients

  • peanut butter: 1/2 cup
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • honey or maple syrup: 1 tablespoon
  • rice vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic (minced): 1 clove
  • water: 3-4 tablespoons
  • sesame oil (optional): 1 teaspoon
